@@TJvDBCustomSearchComboBox.DataResult
Summary
  Contains the names of the field or fields from which to return values when calling GetResult.
Description
  Contains the names of the field or fields from which to return values when calling GetResult. If
  values are to be returned from more than one field, DataResult is a list of field names delimited
  with semicolons.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvDBCustomSearchComboBox.DataSource
Summary
  Links the combo box to a dataset.
Description
  Specify the data source component that identifies the dataset in which the target field is found.
  To allow the combo box to represent the data for a field, both the DataSource and the DataField
  properties must be set.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvDBCustomSearchComboBox.GetResult
Summary
  Retrieves field values from a record that matches the search value.
Description
  Call GetResult to search for a record in the dataset in which the DataField field contains the
  value of the combo box text and return other field values from the found record.
  
  <CODE>
  procedure TForm1.Button1Click(Sender: TObject);
  var
  V: Variant;
  C: Integer;
  A: String;
  begin
  JvDBSearchComboBox.DataResult := 'CustNo;Addr1';
  V := JvDBSearchComboBox.GetResult;
  if not (VarType(V) in [varNull]) then
  begin
    C := V[0];
    A := V[1];
    ShowMessage(IntToStr(C) + #10 + A);
  end
  else
    ShowMessage('Search unsuccessful!'); end; </CODE>

